What is the knowdlege base and bot? 
The knowledge base is being built based upon frequintly asked questions by the community, to supplement the knowledge a bot is being trained using microsoft QnA Maker.

How does the bot work? 
The bot is trained with a knowledge base, this can constantly be updated and the bot will adapt. The bot will be built and deployed through Microsoft Azure services.

Where can I find the bot? 
The aim is to have the bot appear in a chat box when you reach the EOCH website. 

Is it complete?
No, though it should be operational soon.
